# ORIG TITLE    Eurozone remains in recession . 
# ORIG CONTENT  At their latest meeting, Eurozone finance ministers have been trying to boost confidence in the European finance sector. They also released the first instalment of bail-out money for Cyprus . However growth figures from the region shows its problems are far from over. Also on this edition of Business Weekly: European inspectors raid office of some top oil companies and the leading price setter for the industry in a probe into possible price fixing. 
